  !  Javascript(default) is sychroneous and single threaded

  ! execution Context -- executionone line of code at a time
                      -- each operation waits for the last one to complete before executing


  ! Blocking Code VS Non-Blocking Code 
    => Blocking code - Block the flow of program
                     - Read File sychroneous
    
    => Non-Blocking Code - Does not block execution
                         - Read file Async

